data.description: Move-in condition, like new! This immaculate 4 bed, 2.5 bath home offers open floorplan, a covered back patio that overlooks a level, fenced backyard. After purchase the seller added custom shiplap walls & built-in shelves in family room and a sliding barn door to the laundry room. The open kitchen boasts gas cooktop, SS appliances, built-in microwave, large island, and a large breakfast area. Upstairs you will find an oversized primary suite with vaulted ceiling, large walk-in closet, 3 additional secondary bedrooms and a bath with double vanities and tub/shower combo. The large laundry room is conveniently located upstairs. The community is award-winning offering a water park, nature trails, playground and convenient to schools, shopping, restaurants.
